dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer provides an index map that can be used to locate individual scanned map sheets.
dataIdInfo.idAbs: • This polygon shapefile is an index to 1:100,000 scale maps of Halmahera (Indonesia), titled 'Kūchū shashin sokuzu yōzu Harumaheratō jūmanbun no ichi -- Harumaheratō jūmanbun no ichi -- 空中寫真測圖要圖ハルマヘラ島十万分一 -- ハルマヘラ島十万分一/Kūchū shashin sokuzu yōzu Harumaheratō jūmanbun no ichi.’To create this index, footprints were generated using the fishnet tool, and metadata were supplied for the digitized paper maps by Stanford University Libraries. After the footprints were created, the shapefile was trimmed and labeled according to the sources.
dataIdInfo.idCredit: Stanford University Libraries, Stanford Geospatial Center
